	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2015/01/20/keeping-a-lid-on-what-happens-in-davos/" data-title="Keeping a Lid on What Happens in Davos" data-description="Stung by past criticism, organizers of the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, are making an effort to rein in opulent events. ">
